what i think is a NP
((art)?(adj)*(sust))
<DT>?<JJ>*<NN>

example: the little yellow dog barked at the cat
    -the little yellow dog
    -the cat

art             DT      determiner
adj             JJ      adjectives
adj relativo    JJR     relative adjectives
sust            NN      noun
sust propio     NNP     proper noun


other examples:
    -another/DT sharp/JJ dive/NN
    -trade/NN figures/NNS
    -any/DT new/JJ policy/NN measures/NNS
    -earlier/JJR stages/NNS
    -Panamanian/JJ dictator/NN Manuel/NNP Noriega/NNP

better grammar:
((art)?(any kind of adj)*(any kind of sust)+)
<DT>?<JJ.*>*<NN.*>+

more complex examples:
    -his/PRP$ Mansion/NNP House/NNP speech/NN
    -the/DT price/NN cutting/VBG
    -3/CD %/NN to/TO 4/CD %/NN
    -more/JJR than/IN 10/CD %/NN
    -the/DT fastest/JJS developing/VBG trends/NNS
    -'s/POS skill/NN

